erflow-wrap: break-word;">Protein akan membantu dalam membangun kembali otot-ototmu, menjaga sistem kekebalan tubuh dan meningkatkan tingkat energimu untuk mendapatkan tubuh yang sehat kembali.</p><h2 class="article-content-body__item-title" data-component-name="desktop:read-page:article-content-body:section:pagetitle" style="margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 18px; font-family: AcuminPro, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(57, 57, 57); font-size: 24px;">4. Lemak sehat</h2><div class="article-content-body__item-media"><figure class="read-page--photo-gallery--item" id="gallery-image-3158651" data-photo-gallery-page="3" data-image="https://cdn0-production-images-kly.akamaized.net/Ix2VYyMUdDX7Hf9lcB1Ln6b6eMM=/0x597:5831x3883/640x360/filters:quality(75):strip_icc():format(jpeg)/kly-media-production/medias/3158651/original/042885400_1592734110-person-slicing-meat-on-white-chopping-board-1409050.jpg" data-description="Ilustrasi Daging Ikan Salmon Credit: pexels.com/Huy" data-title="Daging Ikan Salmon" data-share-url="https://www.liputan6.com/citizen6/read/5012894/5-makanan-terbaik-untuk-meringankan-gejala-long-covid?photo=3158651" data-photo-id="?photo=3158651" data-copy-link-url="https://www.liputan6.com/citizen6/read/5012894/5-makanan-terbaik-untuk-meringankan-gejala-long-covid" data-component="desktop:read-page:photo-gallery:item" data-component-name="desktop:read-page:photo-gallery:item" style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><div class="read-page--photo-gallery--item__content js-gallery-content" style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; border-radius: 8px; background-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);"><a href="https://www.liputan6.com/citizen6/read/5012894/5-makanan-terbaik-untuk-meringankan-gejala-long-covid#" class="read-page--photo-gallery--item__link" style="color: rgb(255, 51, 0); background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachmen