eberapa waktu tertentu sudah tak dapat lagi diandalkan, seperti saat magrib atau ketika mendung. "Karena mendung tidak bisa diprediksi, kecuali pakai&nbsp;<em>artificial light</em>&nbsp;yang bisa diatur powernya, makin besar power akan makin memengaruhi dimensi&nbsp;<em>lighting</em>&nbsp;di makanan," tambahnya.</p><h2 class="article-content-body__item-title" data-component-name="desktop:read-page:article-content-body:section:pagetitle" style="color: rgb(57, 57, 57); margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 18px; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.4; font-family: AcuminPro, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">3. Angle yang Tepat</h2><div class="article-content-body__item-media"><figure class="read-page--photo-gallery--item" id="gallery-image-2915642" data-photo-gallery-page="3" data-image="https://cdn0-production-images-kly.akamaized.net/7IN1NQ_sYuytzvWIUC3d7MLEkFY=/640x360/smart/filters:quality(75):strip_icc():format(jpeg)/kly-media-production/medias/2915642/original/035853900_1568867476-kobby-mendez-q54Oxq44MZs-unsplash.jpg" data-description="ilustrasi donat/Photo by Kobby Mendez on Unsplash" data-title="makanan manis" data-share-url="https://www.liputan6.com/lifestyle/read/5010284/tips-memotret-makanan-dengan-tampilan-menggiurkan?photo=2915642" data-photo-id="?photo=2915642" data-copy-link-url="https://www.liputan6.com/lifestyle/read/5010284/tips-memotret-makanan-dengan-tampilan-menggiurkan" data-component="desktop:read-page:photo-gallery:item" data-component-name="desktop:read-page:photo-gallery:item" style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><div class="read-page--photo-gallery--item__content js-gallery-content" style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; border-radius: 8px; background-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);"><a href="https://www.liputan6.com/lifestyle/read/5010284/tips-memotret-makanan-dengan-tampilan-menggiurkan#" class="read-page--photo-gallery--item__link" style="background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: 