," katanya.</p><p style="overflow-wrap: break-word;">"Kita harus mencari, misal tidak punya&nbsp;<em>lighting</em>&nbsp;bisa taruh di mana," terang Silva.</p><p style="overflow-wrap: break-word;">Tips selanjutnya adalah memilih&nbsp;<em>angle</em>&nbsp;yang tepat. Silva menjelaskan ia selalu menganjurkan untuk mempelajari&nbsp;<em>angle</em>&nbsp;untuk memotret makanan, misalnya karakter ingin&nbsp;<em>eye level</em>, seperti memotret burger yang ditonjolkan adalah ketebalan roti dan daging.</p><h2 class="article-content-body__item-title" data-component-name="desktop:read-page:article-content-body:section:pagetitle" style="color: rgb(57, 57, 57); margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 18px; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.4; font-family: AcuminPro, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">4. Plating</h2><div class="article-content-body__item-media"><figure class="read-page--photo-gallery--item" id="gallery-image-3981145" data-photo-gallery-page="4" data-image="https://cdn1-production-images-kly.akamaized.net/5459xtXf2GYEZmy97lLZcC-XHsY=/0x54:5184x2976/640x360/filters:quality(75):strip_icc():format(jpeg)/kly-media-production/medias/3981145/original/098035200_1648734220-anna-pelzer-IGfIGP5ONV0-unsplash__3_.jpg" data-description="Ilustrasi Makanan Sehat Credit: unsplash.com/Anna" data-title="Penurunan Kadar Nutrisi Tubuh" data-share-url="https://www.liputan6.com/lifestyle/read/5010284/tips-memotret-makanan-dengan-tampilan-menggiurkan?photo=3981145" data-photo-id="?photo=3981145" data-copy-link-url="https://www.liputan6.com/lifestyle/read/5010284/tips-memotret-makanan-dengan-tampilan-menggiurkan" data-component="desktop:read-page:photo-gallery:item" data-component-name="desktop:read-page:photo-gallery:item" style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><div class="read-page--photo-gallery--item__content js-gallery-content" style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; border-radius: 8px; background-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);"><a href="https://www.liputan6.com